# OpenSpec Feature Workflow

Only apply this rule when the user explicitly asks for this workflow or explicitly names it. Do not treat it as default background behavior.

Use this rule when a feature needs OpenSpec proposal, design, specs, and tasks before implementation.

Required order:

1. Confirm a kebab-case change name.
2. Run `openspec status --change "<change-name>" --json`.
3. Read `openspec instructions <artifact> --change "<change-name>" --json` before each artifact.
4. Complete `proposal.md`, `design.md`, `specs/.../spec.md`, and `tasks.md`.
5. Re-run status until all required artifacts are ready.
